Anyyyyyy day, baby!!!!!

Our last weekend just the 4 of us. Soaking in their little faces because I know soon enough they won’t feel so little anymore 🥹. Dying to find out who this baby is…!!!!! 
I’m honestly 50/50 but if I HAD to guess- here are our final votes!
Mom: boy 💙
Dad: girl 💗
East: boy 💙
Noah: girl 💗

#herecomethenelsons #comeonbaby

Everyone say hi to the newest baby SISTER!!!! Little miss Navy Reign Nelson. She came into this world making us laugh + cry the happiest tears. Weighing 8lb 9oz with the chunkiest rolls and biggest dimples, 19.5in long! Navy girl, you are everything our family needed and more. 😭 IT’S A GIRL! Ahhhhh!!! Still can’t believe it 🫶🏽.

4 years old and the best little daddy 😭 wait for navy’s smile at the end 🥹

Life lately 🤍 what’s everyone up to this summer?! Can’t believe in a week our baby naves will be 6 months old and we’ll be making our first international trip as a fam of 5!!!! Ahhhh a lil nervous but soooo excited. David and I dreamt up this trip and these days while we were dating, so thankful they’re here 🥹. #thesearethedays #herecomethenelsons #family
Sometimes I can’t believe they’re mine 🫶🏽
2016 me is really happy her dreams came true 🥹

A few of my favorite moments from the past two weeks in Europe with our 5, 3 and 6 month old 💛

1. A nakey naves who officially started crawling in Paris 🥐
2. Had a picnic under the twinkling Eiffel Tower 🫶🏽
3. We would never dance in the streets at home but why is everything more romantic in Paris?! 
4. Saw Disneyland Paris and our kids met their idols 🥹
5. Navy after her first taste of gelato 😂☺️
6. We LOVED Lake Como even though we lost nightnight there 😩
7. But especially loved slowing down so much… took a nap on the grass 🙌🏽
8. We took a super fun train to Florence 🤣🫠iykyk and learned how to make pizza and gelato 
9. Saw some weenies and seriously loved the city of Florence
10. My favorite guy in the world 

I wish I could post 1,000 pictures!!! This trip has been everything we needed. I’m forever thankful for these memories with my babies 🥹.

#travel #family #eurotrip
